snippet.textDisplay:
I’ve got a severe ant phobia to the point where I will have a straight up panic attack if I see specific kinds near or on me. (Tiny kitchen black ones cause me anxiety but not a panic attack, but we have a large red species in South East Asia that even thinking about makes me want to cry.)

I’ve been watching your videos as a sort of self-exposure-therapy thing. The phobia is still there but I’ve got a newfound respect for ants and I’m learning so much more about them that I never knew!

Thank you for these videos ^_^
snippet.textOriginal:

I’ve been watching your videos as a sort of self-exposure-therapy thing. The phobia is still there but I’ve got a newfound respect for ants and I’m learning so much more about them that I never knew!
